<s> The problem is probably not with the screen readers, but with the speech synthesis software they are using.  </s>
<s> If they are all relying on the same speech synthesis engine, one can expect that they will all be prone to the same shortcomings in respect of pronunciation accuracy.  </s>
<s> The question, under those circumstances, is whether alternatives are available or a suitable tool could readily be constructed to resolve the problem, as discussed in the working group meeting last month.  </s>
